project.protocols.1.description "Human pancreatic islets were obtained from Prodo or NDRI and recovered in CMRLS at 37°C for 24h-48h hours after receipt. Mouse islets were prepared using gradient centrifugation and islets from the same strain were pooled, then recovered in XX for 24h."
