project.protocols.2.description "Cells were encapsulated using the inDrop platform, into droplets on ice and lysed  in the 4nL microfluidic droplets using a final concentration of 0.4% NP-40. Single cell lysates were subject to reverse transcription at 50°C without purification of RNA (as previously described in Klein et al., Cell 2015)."
